<p>{{Infobox Actor}}</p>
<p><b>Allan Dwan</b> (April 3, 1885 â€“ December 28, 1981) was a pioneering <a href="Canada" title="Canada">Canadian</a>-born American <a href="Film" title="film">motion picture</a> <a href="Film_director" title="film director">director</a>, producer and screenwriter.</p>
